{"tid":559060,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳展鵬自家設計「北斗七星」眼鏡真係好潮　究竟賣出咗幾多副？","createTime":"2018-02-13T00:29:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T04:45:26.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":115,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"31fc510e71df6692567c5e743f59302a3b4d5eca","tid":559060,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T00:29:22.000Z","msg":"陳展鵬的衣著打扮一向都好有獨特個人風格，早前他更榮陞老闆，開設自家設計的太陽眼鏡品牌，計劃打造自己的時裝王國，頭炮就是推出他親自設計的太陽眼鏡系列，一副承惠港幣$1288，雖然價錢唔平，但照樣有粉絲幫襯購買以示支持。<br />\n<br />\n今日乘着TVB Big Big Channel舉辦的《Big Big 明星市集》，被網民捧為「潮流尖端」的陳展鵬更落場開檔推銷自家的「北極光」太陽眼鏡。陳展鵬接受《香港01》訪問時介紹自家設計的太陽眼鏡就說到了背後的故事。「我一直都好想去睇北極光嘅地方，但係一路都冇時間去。呢副眼鏡喺唔同嘅光線底下，就會折射到唔同嘅光出嚟，同埋如果你睇北極光嘅時候，你仲可以睇埋北斗七星，咁你嗰年就一定行好運，所以我就將北斗七星放埋喺眼鏡側邊。」<br />\n<br />\n陳展鵬談到自家品牌「Ruco Vision」的將來發展時，他説：「我冇擺喺店舖度賣，只不過放係自己官網for我啲fans買。我希望我每一年都可以整到一啲product同埋我見到一啲有價值嘅嘢，我都可以做出嚟，例如手機殻，所以唔係淨係眼鏡。」<br />\n<br />\n現場所見，原價$1288的「北極光系列北斗七星太陽眼鏡」變成了$800一副，一定係因為賣眼鏡之餘仲可以幫手做慈善嘅關係先賣平咗咁多啦。陳展鵬仲話呢款太陽眼鏡只係少量製作。睇落真係幾有型，戴咗唔知會唔會可以好似陳展鵬咁有型呢？至於副眼鏡有幾多人買過？陳展鵬就好婉轉咁講：「幫我做眼鏡嘅朋友就話點樣訂都有，當然如果fans鍾意而又帶得舒服嘅話，其實可以再訂嘅。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/159006/thumbnail/0c8831a22900e66fdde60534ca690bed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F159006%2Fthumbnail%2F0c8831a22900e66fdde60534ca690bed.jpg&h=14c66363&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1200214/xlarge/e417fd74798343ee949758ef1b20cedd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1200214%2Fxlarge%2Fe417fd74798343ee949758ef1b20cedd.jpg&h=d2117209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/159006/%E9%99%B3%E5%B1%95%E9%B5%AC%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%B6%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88-%E5%8C%97%E6%96%97%E4%B8%83%E6%98%9F-%E7%9C%BC%E9%8F%A1%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E5%A5%BD%E6%BD%AE-%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E8%B3%A3%E5%87%BA%E5%92%97%E5%B9%BE%E5%A4%9A%E5%89%AF-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F159006%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25B1%2595%25E9%25B5%25AC%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E8%25A8%2588-%25E5%258C%2597%25E6%2596%2597%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%2598%259F-%25E7%259C%25BC%25E9%258F%25A1%25E7%259C%259F%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E6%25BD%25AE-%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E7%25AB%259F%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2592%2597%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2589%25AF-&d=naZqUvrmHkgCcgPIqat5xr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=42eb66b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/159006/%E9%99%B3%E5%B1%95%E9%B5%AC%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%B6%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88-%E5%8C%97%E6%96%97%E4%B8%83%E6%98%9F-%E7%9C%BC%E9%8F%A1%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E5%A5%BD%E6%BD%AE-%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E8%B3%A3%E5%87%BA%E5%92%97%E5%B9%BE%E5%A4%9A%E5%89%AF-</a>"},{"pid":"c0ac7d0afd5af12c451e1719a97734d6fe5e85f5","tid":559060,"uid":82917,"like":175,"dislike":6,"score":169,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T00:31:20.000Z","msg":"我係首席鵬友，買左兩副，超好睇喔。"},{"pid":"14528b62b755fb3194ca9b4e12594ccfe2d19c0b","tid":559060,"uid":21423,"like":104,"dislike":201,"score":-97,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T00:34:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2cb7852b583340916aea222e9620fb0440c99d82","tid":559060,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T00:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169b4e97a56a1a962d570b69aee9d191049652dd","tid":559060,"uid":115910,"like":133,"dislike":10,"score":123,"quote":{"pid":"14528b62b755fb3194ca9b4e12594ccfe2d19c0b","tid":559060,"uid":21423,"like":104,"dislike":201,"score":-97,"quote":{"pid":"c0ac7d0afd5af12c451e1719a97734d6fe5e85f5","tid":559060,"uid":82917,"like":175,"dislike":6,"score":169,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T00:31:20.000Z","msg":"我係首席鵬友，買左兩副，超好睇喔。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T00:34:57.000Z","msg":"此